snippet.title: CleanSheet Soccer - Launch Trailer | PS VR2 & PSVR Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10009801

CleanSheet Soccer debuts on #PSVR2 this May 16! Embrace the challenge of stopping shots from motion-captured pros. Set your own weekly fitness goals, and track how many calories you've burned while blocking thousands of shots. Your journey to goalkeeping greatness starts here!
